# Email Sending

Vercel blocks outbound SMTP. Resend free tier only sends to the signup email. Use **Web3Forms**.

## Pattern (server-side API route)

```ts
const res = await fetch('https://api.web3forms.com/submit', {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', Accept: 'application/json' },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    access_key: process.env.WEB3FORMS_KEY,
    subject:    `[Al-Amir] ${subject}`,
    from_name:  name,
    email:      email,   // becomes Reply-To
    message:    message,
    botcheck:   '',      // honeypot — must be empty string
  }),
});
const data = await res.json();
if (!data.success) throw new Error('Web3Forms failed');
```

## Config
- Env var: `WEB3FORMS_KEY` (set in Vercel dashboard and `.env.local`)
- Get key at: web3forms.com/create — enter `info@alamiric.org`, verify the email, copy the key
- No domain DNS changes needed — just one-time email verification
- Delivers directly to `info@alamiric.org`
